settings.title: What is the Membership?
settings.desc: Membership is HTVRONT’s exclusive rewards program that’ll give you ALL the good vibes. Earn points to cash in for free products or discounts on your next order!

settings.title: How to join HTVRONT membership?
settings.desc: Only need to successfully register an account, you can join HTVRONT membership for free, and get 300 registration points to start your reward redemption immediately!

settings.title: How do I earn points?
settings.desc:
When you join the Membership, you'll earn points when you purchase any products! The number of points you earn are based on your membership tier:
#Bronze members earn 5 points for every $1.00 spent.
#Silver members earn 7.5 points for every $1.00 spent.
#Gold members earn 10 points for every $1.00 spent.
A few more things to note:
Points are calculated based on the subtotal of your purchase after any discounts have been applied.
You don’t earn points for dollars spent on applicable taxes, shipping or handling.
When products are returned for a refund to the original payment method, points will be deducted from your account for the amount of the return, net of taxes, shipping and handling.

settings.title: Can I earn points without purchasing anything?
settings.desc:
Yes! We offer a ton of different opportunities to earn points!
Here are just a few different ways you can earn them:
Creating an account = 300 points
Birthday bonus = 200 points
Signing up for our newsletter = 100 points
Following us on Instagram = 25 points
Following us on Facebook = 25 points
Leave a Review = 20 points
Refer a Friends = 200 points

settings.title: What can I redeem points for?
settings.desc:
You can redeem points for free products and discounts on orders! Offers include:
Redeeming Products:
200 points = 1 Transfer tape 12×5ft
500 points = 1 Permanent vinyl 12×5ft
1000 points = 1 Heat transfer vinyl 12×10ft
3000 points = 1 Easy press mini
And other products...
Redeeming Discounts:
500 points = $5.00 off
1000 points = $10.00 off
2000 points = $20.00 off
3000 points = $30.00 off

settings.title: What are the HTVRONT Membership Tiers?
settings.desc:
HTVRONT has 3 membership tiers:
The #Bronze Tier: ($1-$499 spent)
When you create an account through our website, you’ll automatically be enrolled in the #Bronze membership tier and Insider Email List!
The #Silver Tier: ($500-$999 spent)
If you spend between $500-$999 & Complete 1 Referral & Make 8 Purchases, you’ll be enrolled in the #Sliver membership tier! In addition to earning points, you’ll also gain early access to sales and products!
The #Gold Tier: ($1000 or more spent)
If you spend $1000 & Complete 3 Referrals & Make 15 Purchases or more (amazing!), you’ll be enrolled in the #Gold membership tier! In addition to earning points, you'll gain early access to sales and enjoy exclusive fast shipping & delivery!

settings.title: Will my Member Points be cleared?
settings.desc:
Your membership tier is based on the amount you spend within a rolling 12-month period.
For example, suppose you spend $500 on products. In that case, you'll be enrolled as a #Silver for 12 months from the original date of purchase. You must spend at least an additional $500 during those 12 months of being a #Silver to remain in that tier. If you spend less than $500, your membership tier will automatically adjust to the correct level based on the amount you paid in that period.
Member points will automatically expire 12 months from the date they are earned. It's your responsibility to monitor your account and point status.

settings.title: On which country can member points be used?
settings.desc:
Currently, only US users can redeem points on US websites. 
Users who have member points but not in the US region are currently unable to use them. We will keep your points and it can be used when we open websites in your region.

settings.video_title: 1st Heat Press with Auto Pressure Control
settings.video_text: Intelligent pressure control & uniform heating make heat transfer & sublimation simpler and more enjoyable than ever before.

settings.explain_title: Creativity Unleashed in Just One Click
settings.explain_text: Heat transfer and sublimation have never been easier than with HTVRONT Auto Heat Press. No assembly, complicated setup, or difficult press-to-lock is required, all you have to do is plug it in, place heat transfer projects, and click a button to start.

HTVRONT's advanced pressure system allows it to automatically auto-adjust to the thickness of materials up to 2.5 cm/ 1 inch. That way, you do not have to test the pressure again and again for various items. HTVRONT takes care of the work for you.

This machine can monitor and control the temperature of the heating plate accurately and ensure fast and uniform heating across the plate. Heating plate will reach the max temp of 210°C in less than 6 minutes,which is almost twice as fast as a typical heat press.

workspace adopts a pullout drawer design, so you don't have to worry about the heat source hovering over your hands and the potential to get burned as you work. Whenever the device is not being used for 10 minutes, it automatically shuts down to prevent overheating hazards.

settings.explain_content: HTVRONT is a collection development, production, and sales in one of the handmade DIY materials & equipment manufacturing enterprises. It attaches great importance to R&D investment and innovation and has formed its own set of standards in HTV production.

settings.channelmain_text: Inspired by the passion of many innovative craft enthusiasts, we're committed to working on more advanced materials, tools, and machines in handicraft. As one of Sijiu Tech's brands, established on 9th April 2018, we provide multiple DIY choices to make crafting easier than ever, which has already become our greatest wish and mission.

We provide not only excellent complements of DIY creation but also the best customer service and mutual benefits for our partners. Alongside the passion for handcrafts, sincerity to our customers, and devotion as our brand's core values, we endeavor to create a harmonizing and user-friendly atmosphere. And this is part of the reason why HTVRONT is your perfect and most considerate DIY companion.

"Accessible, durable, and affordable." Having our productions recognized by most customers, we feel empowered and responsible for a better product experience. Global supply chains plus convenient warehouse and logistics system, over 12000² meters independent production R&D workshop, application on mugs, tees, etc. Based on our greatest mission, we're dedicated to building a global DIY materials shopping platform with manufacturing, research, and trade integration.

settings.rules_main:
Participation:

1.Click “Like” on the voting page to vote for your favorite patterns.

2.You can vote for three patterns in a round.

3.Click “Like” again to cancel your vote.

Vote:

1. Click "Like" for your favorite pattern. When the number of "Like" reaches the goal, we will produce the HTV of the specific pattern.

2. We will display various patterns in each round. You can click "Like" for three patterns, but once only for each pattern.

3. After each round of voting, the patterns that reach the goal will be produced as Heat Transfer Vinyl, and others not chosen will be taken down.

Prize:

1. Once the pattern reaches the goals, the project backers will get a $10 (no min. spend) coupon on the HTVRONT website (Not suitable for machines and pre-sale products).

2. When the HTV of the chosen pattern goes public, the project backers will enjoy the priority of purchasing and a 30% OFF discount coupon.

*One coupon for one purchase only. Each backer will get only one for each coupon.

settings.FAQ_content: Prices will vary based on the pattern.

a. Once the patterns reach the goals, we will send backers a $10 (no min. spend) coupon on the HTVRONT website (Not suitable for machines and pre-sale products).

b. When the new patterned products are about to be launched, we will send an invitation email to the backers so that they can enjoy the priority of purchasing and a 30% OFF discount coupon.

*One coupon for one purchase only. Each backer will get only one for each coupon.
We will ship the product within three days after placing an order.
You can search for "pattern" on our website to purchase or contact our customer service to help you place an order.

settings.FAQ_subtitle: How to check my vote history?
settings.FAQ_content: You can check the patterns you voted on the “My votes” page.

settings.FAQ_subtitle: How to check my vote history?

settings.FAQheader_text: To align with the environmental-friendly concept and reduce unnecessary production and waste, we launched a "Co-Creation Project" campaign. By conducting an online pattern poll, we hand over the production rights to you - you can help decide what products we produce and how much we make. From the conception of each pattern, selection, HTV production, purchase, and receives the products, this process will be created by you and HTVRONT. It, therefore, helps enhance material utilization, reduce production pollution, and cut backlogs. We hope to build a beautiful eco-environment and save nature together with you.
settings.FAQmain_title: How to get the product launch notification?
settings.FAQmain_text: The "Co-Creation Project" will take 15-30 days for you to vote for your favorite patterns. After each round of voting, we will notify the project backers via email and send a $10 (no min. spend) coupon simultaneously. When the new products go public, we will send an email to invite you to purchase and offer you a 30% OFF discount.
